hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, `Детальный`, 1, `Простой`, 0, `Откл.`
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then hideparameter "gs_resol" lock "gs_resol" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
values "screenSize" stScreenSize[1], stScreenSize[3], stScreenSize[2], stScreenSize[4] values "iScreenSize" 1, 2, 3, 4 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "screenSize" then if screenSize = stScreenSize[1] then iScreenSize = 1 if screenSize = stScreenSize[2] then iScreenSize = 2 if screenSize = stScreenSize[3] then iScreenSize = 3 if screenSize = stScreenSize[4] then iScreenSize = 4 parameters iScreenSize = iScreenSize else if iScreenSize = 1 then screenSize = stScreenSize[1] if iScreenSize = 2 then screenSize = stScreenSize[2] if iScreenSize = 3 then screenSize = stScreenSize[3] if iScreenSize = 4 then screenSize = stScreenSize[4] parameters screenSize = screenSize endif
if useFactoryMats then lock "frameMat", "backMat", "standMat", "logoMat" hideparameter "frameMat", "backMat", "standMat", "logoMat" endif
lock "a", "b", "zzyzx"
if pic then lock "screenMat" hideparameter "screenMat" else lock "gs_picture_custom", "gs_picture_name" hideparameter "gs_picture_custom", "gs_picture_name" endif if not(gs_picture_custom) then lock "gs_picture_name" hideparameter "gs_picture_name" endif
Symbol.Comment: iMac различных размеров и со специальным рисунком на экране.
